<entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-3476358971570196875</id><published>2016-04-13T22:18:52.484+08:00</published><updated>2016-04-13T22:18:52.484+08:00</updated><title type='text'>多态应该没什么缺点。有缺点的是继承。有句话是prefer Aggregation/Compositi...</title><content type='html'>多态应该没什么缺点。有缺点的是继承。有句话是prefer Aggregation/Composition over inheritance。 具体实例是：因为继承树不仅可以竖向扩展,还会出现横向扩展的情况,甚至还会出现往与其它维垂直方向的第三维,第四维...第n维方向扩展。所以如果用继承则会造成hierarchy的臃肿。不恰当的比方是：&lt;br /&gt;House DogHouse CatHouse WoodenDogHouse WoodenCatHouse RockDogHouse RockCatHouse &lt;br /&gt;... WoodenCatHouseForWindows WoodenDogHouseForMac ...&lt;br /&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/5886745261051592443/comments/default/3476358971570196875'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/5886745261051592443/comments/default/3476358971570196875'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/01/defect-of-java-beginner-2-oo.html?showComment=1460557132484#c3476358971570196875' title=''/><author><name>Anonymous</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/01/defect-of-java-beginner-2-oo.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-5886745261051592443' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/5886745261051592443' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1965374250"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2016年4月13日 下午10:18:00"/></entry>
